   b. **FOLLOW PATTERN** (High Priority): If organized subdirectory structure exists → CREATE in appropriate subdirectory
   c. **ROOT ONLY IF** (Fallback): Only create at docs/ root if NO subdirectory structure exists
   d. **NEVER CREATE DUPLICATES**: Never create docs/FILE.md if docs/subdir/FILE.md exists

4. **Examples of Correct Behavior**:
   - ✅ GOOD: docs/user/USER_GUIDE.md exists → UPDATE docs/user/USER_GUIDE.md (not create docs/USER_GUIDE.md)
